#
# Instructions:
# 1. Download and install the Android NDK.
# 2. Run ccmake -DVTK_ANDROID_BUILD=ON /path/to/vtk/source
# 3. Set ANDROID_NDK to be the path to the NDK. (/opt/android-ndk by default)
# 4. Set API level and architecture.
# 5. Generate and make
